<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css" />
  <style>
    /* Custom CSS styles */
    .about-image {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: auto; /* Adjust this value as needed */
      height: auto;
      display: block;
    }

    .about-content {
      margin-left: 10px;
    }

    .about-content p {
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #280404c7; /* Adjust the color as needed */
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body tabindex="-1">
  <!-- Include navbar partial -->
  <% include('partials/navbar', { page: '/about' }) %>

  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <div class="hero bg-base-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="hero-content text-center">
        <div class="max-w-md">
          <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">About</h1>
          <p class="py-6">Everything you want to know about me - the designer &amp; developer.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <br />

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-center">
      <div>
        <!-- Image with 16:9 aspect ratio -->
        <img class="about-image" src="/aboutme.jpg" alt="About Me" />
      </div>
      <div class="about-content">
        <p class="py-6">
          Hello there! I'm Devankit, currently pursuing my studies in Computer Programming and Analysis at Seneca College.
          I've always been fascinated by the world of technology and computers, which led me to embark on this exciting
          journey of learning how to code and develop software. Alongside my academic pursuits, I also enjoy representing
          my college as an extramural player for the Seneca College cricket team, where I get to showcase my skills and
          passion for sports. With my knowledge in website building and a deep understanding of programming, I'm constantly
          seeking new challenges and opportunities to grow both personally and professionally. Join me as I navigate through
          the realms of programming, web development, and beyond!
        </p>
        <p>
          Apart from my academic and extracurricular interests, I am also passionate about exploring different cultures
          and cuisines. Traveling to new places and trying out diverse foods allows me to broaden my perspective and
          appreciate the beauty of diversity. Whether it's savoring street food in bustling markets or dining at fine
          restaurants, I enjoy the culinary adventures that come with exploring new destinations.
        </p>
        <p>
          Furthermore, I have a keen interest in arts and creativity. In my free time, you'll often find me experimenting
          with photography, sketching, or exploring other forms of artistic expression. Engaging in creative activities
          helps me relax and unwind, while also stimulating my imagination and fostering innovation in my work.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
